  "category": "energy-optimization",
  "gradingType": "automated",
  "prompt": "Read network.json describing a 5-bus DC power system. Compute DC power flow: (1) set bus 0 (slack) angle to 0, (2) generator at bus 3 produces 60 MW, (3) solve for bus voltage angles using DC power flow equations P_ij = (theta_i - theta_j) / x_ij, (4) compute line flows. Write power_flow.json with: bus_angles (array of 5 angles in radians), line_flows (array of 6 flow values in MW, positive = from→to direction), generation (array: bus 0 slack output, bus 3 = 60).",
